<item>
            <title>[HBASE-5322] RetriesExhaustedException: Trying to contact region server</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5322</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have a hbase table which holds data for more than 10GB. Now I used the same client scanner to scan which fails and reports,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;Could not seek StoreFileScanner[HFileScanner for reader reader=hdfs&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue occurs only for the table which holds huge data and not for tables holding small data.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
